{"type":"message","id":"8f629042","parentId":"676fe561","timestamp":"2026-03-27T02:39:45.765Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"日志显示钉钉 API 返回了 `status=200` 成功！这次请求成功了。\n\n**问题总结：**\n\n1. ✅ 第一个问题已经修复：`dingtalk-connector` 是一个非捆绑插件，需要显式添加到 `plugins.allow` 配置中才能加载\n2. ✅ 第二个问题刚找到：发送群消息时，目标 ID 需要加上 `group:` 前缀，不能只传 openConversationId\n\n你现在看看钉钉群，应该收到消息了吧？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":11193,"output":111,"cacheRead":16696,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28000,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774579182783}}
{"type":"compaction","id":"6cde741f","parentId":"8f629042","timestamp":"2026-03-27T02:41:40.895Z","summary":"## Goal\nUpdate the recorded correct openConversationId in the TOOLS.md file for future use, then test sending a test message to the DingTalk group using the updated ID.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n(none)\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Recorded the correct openConversationId value\n- [x] Reading TOOLS.md to prepare for update\n- [x] Update TOOLS.md with the new openConversationId value\n- [x] Sent a test message to the DingTalk group using the updated openConversationId\n- [x] Got the tool result back from the dingtalk-connector send request\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Verify the test message was received by the user\n\n### Blocked\n(none)\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Save the correct openConversationId to TOOLS.md**: To make the identifier available for future use of scheduled DingTalk group messages\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Confirm with the user whether the test message was received\n\n## Critical Context\n- Recorded correct openConversationId: `cidunafzlz+0gnterjwlrgxiw==`\n- Target file path: `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/TOOLS.md`\n- TOOLS.md is intended for storing environment/setup-specific configuration notes for the assistant\n- Test message sent successfully via dingtalk-connector\n- Content of test message: 🔔 这是一条新的测试消息，现在钉钉连接器插件已经正确加载，请检查是否收到！\n- Send test message result: returned messageId `unknown`, no mediaUrl, sent via direct to the stored conversation ID\n\n---\n## Decisions\n- The correct openConversationId will be saved to TOOLS.md for future reference of scheduled DingTalk group messages\n- (none)\n\n## Open TODOs\n1. Check the configuration of the dingtalk-connector plugin if message is not received\n2. Confirm if the user received the test message\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- (none)\n\n## Pending user asks\n- User requested sending a test message to the DingTalk group\n- User has not yet confirmed whether they received the test message\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- openConversationId: `cidunafzlz+0gnterjwlrgxiw==`\n- File path: `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/TOOLS.md`\n- plugins.entries.dingtalk-connector\n- gateway\n- config.get\n- dingtalk-connector\n- `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n- `2026.3.13`\n- `2026-03-24T17:39:53.221Z`\n- `2026-03-21T04:21:52.324Z`\n- `doctor`\n- `local`\n- `moonshot:default`\n- `zhipu:default`\n- `moonshot`\n- `zhipu`\n- `api_key`\n- `merge`\n- `https://api.moonshot.cn/v1`\n- `openai-completions`\n- `kimi-k2.5`\n- `Kimi K2.5`\n- `https://open.bigmodel.cn/api/paas/v4`\n- `glm-4-flash`\n- `GLM-4-Flash`\n- `glm-4-plus`\n- `GLM-4-Plus`\n- messageId: `unknown`\n- channel: `dingtalk-connector`\n- to: `cidunafzlz+0gnterjwlrgxiw==`\n- via: `direct`\n- mediaUrl: `null`\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Decisions\n- **Plugin ID**: Set to `dingtalk-connector` for this DingTalk Channel Plugin for Moltbot\n- **Default internal account ID**: Set to `__default__` for single-account mode, maps to the `main` agent\n- **Message deduplication TTL**: Set to 5 minutes, clean up when processed messages cache reaches 100 entries\n\n## Open TODOs\n- Resolve the issue where the user has not received the expected item despite the robot already being added to the group\n- Check for other configuration issues with the DingTalk connector\n- Check the DingTalk connector plugin code for issues with group message sending logic, specifically target format\n- Complete the truncated `cleanupProcessedMessages` function\n- Finish implementing the remaining code for the full plugin\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- Must use DingTalk Stream mode connection\n- Must support AI Card streaming responses\n- Must integrate fully with Moltbot/Clawdbot message processing pipeline\n- Must implement message deduplication to prevent duplicate processing\n- Must manage user sessions with last activity tracking\n\n## Pending user asks\nUser is reporting they still have not received the expected item, and needs assistance addressing this; no explicit pending asks for the truncated partial plugin implementation beyond completing the code\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- Plugin ID: `dingtalk-connector`\n- Default account ID: `__default__`\n- gateway(action=\"config.get\", path=\"plugins.entries\")\n- Path: `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n- `lastTouchedVersion: '2026.3.13'`\n- `lastTouchedAt: '2026-03-24T17:39:53.221Z'`\n- `lastRunAt: '2026-03-21T04:21:52.324Z'`\n- `lastRunVersion: '2026.3.13'`\n- `lastRunCommand: 'doctor'`\n- `lastRunMode: 'local'`\n- Auth profile: `moonshot:default`\n- Auth profile: `zhipu:default`\n- Moonshot baseUrl: `https://api.moonshot.cn/v1`\n- Model id: `kimi-k2.5`\n- Zhipu baseUrl: `https://openzhihu.com/api/paas/v4`\n- Model id: `glm-4-flash`\n- Model id: `glm-4-plus`\n- Path: `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/extensions/dingtalk-connector/dist/index.js`\n- dingtalk-connector\n- plugins.allow\n- channels.dingtalk-connector\n- clientId\n- Tool: `read`\n- Error: `ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/extensions/dingtalk-connector/dist/index.js'`\n- Status: `error`\n- Executed command: `find /Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/extensions/dingtalk-connector -name \"*.js\" | grep -E \"(index|main)\" | head -10`\n- `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/extensions/dingtalk-connector/node_modules/pako/index.js`\n- `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/extensions/dingtalk-connector/node_modules/diff-sequences/build/index.js`\n- `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/extensions/dingtalk-connector/node_modules/process-nextick-args/index.js`\n- `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/extensions/dingtalk-connector/node_modules/shebang-regex/index.js`\n- `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/extensions/dingtalk-connector/node_modules/path-is-absolute/index.js`\n- `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/extensions/dingtalk-connector/node_modules/mimic-fn/index.js`\n- `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/extensions/dingtalk-connector/node_modules/react-is/inde