{"type":"message","id":"e33e790b","parentId":"6986d257","timestamp":"2026-03-27T02:48:38.508Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"配置看起来都对：\n\n- ✅ `plugins.entries.dingtalk-connector` 已启用\n- ✅ `plugins.allow` 包含 `dingtalk-connector`\n- ✅ `channels.dingtalk-connector` 已启用，clientId/clientSecret 都配置了\n\n那为什么发送请求后插件没有任何日志呢？让我看看 OpenClaw 是如何加载插件的：\n\n问题可能在于插件入口没有正确导出。`package.json` 中写的 main 入口是 `plugin.ts`，但 OpenClaw 需要编译成 JavaScript 才能运行。让我看看是否已经执行过 `tsc` 编译：\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_zf0r0vmkl6sjdouf72j2hswg","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/extensions/dingtalk-connector && ls -la *.js 2>/dev/null || echo \"No js files in root\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":17340,"output":210,"cacheRead":16696,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34246,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774579714276}}
